Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
I came here to shop, but the selection is most
disappointing.

<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
The products here are of decent quality. I believe
I'll come again.

<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
I was able to find a lot of what I've been looking
for here. This place...has a fine selection. I'm
lucky to have come.

<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
I like this town best of all. It's quite well-known
in social circles, and with good reason.

<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
I love the guild here. Everyone who works there
is so passionate! Makes me happy every time I
drop by.

<NAME_MOB_TENZING>
Whenever a trader comes to my house, this
town's guild invariably comes up in
conversation. It is quite famous.
